data.description: Lake living in the lap of luxury! You will fall in love with the view from every corner of this home! Entertain on the deck featuring an automatic awning system or the oversized sun-room before bringing your guests to the theatre found on the lower level adjacent to the 26x21 family room! Four bedrooms mean you'll always have room for guests! Oversized utility and storage areas, a John Deere room mean you'll have space for everything! Store your boat in the 27x21 recreation garage before using the neighborhood boat slip for the perfect day on the lake!
